<div class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About Bracket Maker Builder</h1>
    <p class="lead">The ultimate tool for creating and managing tournament brackets</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Bracket Maker Builder was created to simplify the process of organizing and managing
          tournaments of all sizes. Whether you're running a local sports league, an office
          competition, or a large-scale tournament, our platform provides the tools you need
          to create professional, engaging brackets.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li><strong>Intuitive Design:</strong> Create brackets in minutes with our user-friendly interface</li>
          <li><strong>Real-time Updates:</strong> Participants can follow tournament progress live</li>
          <li><strong>Customization:</strong> Brand your tournaments with custom colors, logos, and styling</li>
          <li><strong>Mobile Support:</strong> Manage tournaments on the go with our mobile app</li>
          <li><strong>Multiple Formats:</strong> Support for single elimination, double elimination, and round robin</li>
          <li><strong>Voting Brackets:</strong> Engage audiences with interactive voting tournaments</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Create Your Bracket</h3>
              <p>Choose your tournament format and add teams or participants</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Customize & Share</h3>
              <p>Personalize your bracket design and share it with participants</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Track Progress</h3>
              <p>Update results and let everyone follow the tournament live</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Perfect For</h2>
        <div class="use-cases">
          <div class="use-case">
            <h3>Sports Tournaments</h3>
            <p>Basketball, soccer, tennis, and any competitive sport</p>
          </div>

          <div class="use-case">
            <h3>Gaming Competitions</h3>
            <p>Esports tournaments, video game competitions, board game contests</p>
          </div>

          <div class="use-case">
            <h3>Office Events</h3>
            <p>March Madness pools, fantasy leagues, team building activities</p>
          </div>

          <div class="use-case">
            <h3>Educational Events</h3>
            <p>Academic competitions, debate tournaments, science fairs</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="sidebar">
          <div class="stats-card">
            <h3>By the Numbers</h3>
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">50K+</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Brackets Created</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">500K+</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Participants</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">10K+</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Active Users</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-card">
            <h3>Get In Touch</h3>
            <p>Have questions or need help with your tournament?</p>
            <a href="mailto:support@bracketmakerbuilder.com" class="btn btn-primary">
              Contact Support
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p>Create your first bracket today and see why thousands choose our platform.</p>
      <%= link_to "Start Building", root_path(anchor: "bracket-builder"), class: "btn btn-primary btn-large" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
